{
  "id": "adv_love_2405_08_02",
  "title": "Episode 8 Part 2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lovehroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lovehroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――高校一年生　十一月",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――November‚ 1st year of high school",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "必ずまた会いに行くと約束する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh008.m4a",
              "text": "あのさ、芽衣\n実は冬休みにそっちに行こうと\n思ってるんだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Hey‚ Mei. Actually‚ I'm thinking of\ngoing there during winter break.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 112.5666672309,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 118.1000010729
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh009.m4a",
              "text": "これからバイトをして旅費を稼ぐよ\nそれで冬休みにそっちに行って\n君と一緒に年越しをしたい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm going to start working part-time\nto earn money for the trip. I want\nto go there during winter break and\nspend New Year's Eve with you.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 118.1000010729,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei008.m4a",
              "text": "え？　でも、部活で忙しいんじゃ……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Eh? But aren't you busy with club\nactivities…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 125.6000031074,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh010.m4a",
              "text": "陸上部を続けながらバイトもやるよ\n冬休みだけじゃない\n長期休みの度にそっちに行くよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'll work part-time while continuing\nwith the track team. Not just winter\nbreak‚ I'll come see you during\nevery long break.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 129.800005142,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei009.m4a",
              "text": "それ、いい考えだねー！\nよーっし、それじゃあ芽衣も\nお金を貯めて会いに行こうかな！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "That's a great idea~! Alright‚ then\nMei will save up money to come see\nyou too!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 136.9333496651,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei010.m4a",
              "text": "こうして電話で話すよりも\n直接会った方がいいもんね～",
              "translations": {
                "en": "It's better to see each other in\nperson than to talk on the phone\nlike this~.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 145.4666718087,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 149.5333130441
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": null,
              "speakerName": "",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "――高校一年生　十二月",
              "translations": {
                "en": "――December‚ 1st year of high school",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 150.433317566,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 152.199993388
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "（あれから俺は部活と勉強\nそしてバイトを両立させながら\n田舎へと向かう準備を進めた）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "(From then on‚ I juggled club\nactivities‚ studies‚ and part-time\nwork while preparing to go to the\ncountryside.)",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 153.0666555328,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "（そしてついに冬休みとなり\n俺は芽衣に会うために\n田舎へとやってきたのだった）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "(Finally‚ winter break arrived‚ and\nI came to the countryside to see\nMei.)",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 162.8999939523,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 6166.682378299982
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei011.m4a",
              "text": "{user}くーん！\n久しぶり～！　元気にしてたー？\n芽衣はね、とーっても――",
              "translations": {
                "en": "{user}-kun~! Long time no see~!\nHow have you been~? Mei has been~\nreally~",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 170.5333578033,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 6766.65852870002
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 176.7807275695
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣っ……！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Mei!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 177.300016332,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 178.3333466136
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei012.m4a",
              "text": "わっ！　も、も～\nいきなりぎゅーってされたら\nびっくりしちゃうよ～",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Wah! S-suddenly hugging me like that\nwill surprise me~!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 178.3333466136,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "ごめん。でも、こうして会えたのが\n本当に嬉しくて、つい……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Sorry. But I'm so happy to see you\nagain‚ I couldn't help myself…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 186.9333466136,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei013.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣も、君に会えて嬉しいよ！\n久しぶりの{user}君だ～\nぽかぽかしてて気持ちいいな～",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm happy to see you too! It's been\na while‚ {user}-kun. You're so\nwarm and comfy.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 192.566679947,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei014.m4a",
              "text": "会ったら何を言おうかなって\nずーっと毎日考えてたんだけど……\n嬉し過ぎて全部忘れちゃった。あはは",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I was thinking about what to say to\nyou every day… but I'm so happy I\nforgot everything. Ahaha.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 204.6000132803,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "あのさ、芽衣\n俺、君に言うことがあるんだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Hey‚ Mei. I have something to tell\nyou.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 216.6666768952,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei015.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣に言うこと？\nえ～？　なんだろう～？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Something to tell me? Ehh? What is\nit?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 221.7666901195,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "俺、高校を卒業したらこの町に\n引っ越そうと思ってる。だから……\nその時は俺と一緒に暮らしてくれないか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm planning to move to this town\nafter I graduate high school. So…\nwill you live with me then?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 226.8000214183,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 235.5350390041
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei016.m4a",
              "text": "えぇっ！？　い、一緒にって……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Ehhh!? T-together…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 236.2333608553,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 239.9666941886
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "俺は、芽衣とずっと一緒にいたい\nだ、だから……これからは\n結婚を前提に、付き合ってほしい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I want to be with you forever‚ Mei.\nS-so… I want us to date with the\nintention of getting married.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 239.9666941886,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei017.m4a",
              "text": "……うん！　もちろんだよ～！\nすっごく嬉しい！！\n芽衣の方こそ、よろしくね？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Yes! Of course~! I'm so happy!! I'm\nlooking forward to it!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 248.8333659416,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei018.m4a",
              "text": "結婚、結婚かぁ\n{user}君と結婚したら\n毎日楽しいんだろうね～",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Marriage… I see‚ marriage… It would\nbe so much fun every day if I\nmarried {user}-kun.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 258.5333496655,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei019.m4a",
              "text": "一緒のお家に住んで、子供もいーっぱいで\n楽しい家族にしたいな～\nあ……芽衣、いいこと思いついた！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "We'll live in the same house‚ have\nlots of kids‚ and be a happy\nfamily~. Ah… I have a great idea!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 267.1333862866,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 18266.618291099974
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 273.3999964396
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 277.5667175854
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei020.m4a",
              "text": "結婚って何歳から出来たんだっけ……？\n芽衣達、もう結婚って出来る！？\n今から婚姻届取りに行こうよ！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "What age can you get married…? Can\nwe get married already!? Let's go\nget our marriage registration right\nnow!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 277.5667175854,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "あ、おい！　ちょっと、待てって！\n俺の手をそんなに強く引っ張るなって！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Hey‚ wait! Don't pull my hand so\nhard!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 286.366723689,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "別れることを伝える",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 293.3333903557
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh019.m4a",
              "text": "なぁ、芽衣\nやっぱりこのままじゃダメだと思うんだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Hey‚ Mei. I don't think this is\ngoing to work.",
                "id": ""
              },
