            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh020.m4a",
              "text": "俺のせいで芽衣が寂しい思いをするのは\n嫌なんだ。だから……俺達、もう別れよう",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I don't want you to feel lonely\nbecause of me‚ Mei. So… let's break\nup.",
                "id": ""
