              "startTime": 299.2000570224,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei021.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣は君のこと好きだよ？\n{user}君は、もう……\n芽衣のこと好きじゃない……のかな？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "But Mei likes you? Don't you… like\nMei anymore…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 307.8000407463,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh021.m4a",
              "text": "そんなことはない！\nでも、このまま俺に付き合わせてたら\n芽衣にいつか嫌な思いをさせそうで……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "That's not true! But I'm afraid that\nif we keep dating‚ you'll eventually\nbe unhappy…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 321.1333537345,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei022.m4a",
              "text": "……そっか\n{user}君だっていろいろと\n考えたんだよね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…I see. You've thought about a lot\nof things‚ haven't you‚\n{user}-kun.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 329.7333293204,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei023.m4a",
              "text": "分かったよ\nそれじゃあ、芽衣達別れよっか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Okay. Then… shall we break up?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 338.8666952057,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-mei024.m4a",
              "text": "今までありがとね、{user}君\n凄く楽しかったよ。……ばいばい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Thank you for everything‚\n{user}-kun. I had a lot of fun.\n…Goodbye.",
                "id": ""
