              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_02-koh023.m4a",
              "text": "久しぶり、芽衣\n元気そうで何よりだよ",
