              "text": "いいね～。行こう行こう！　実はね……\n{user}君が戻って来た時の\nために君の釣り竿も作ってたんだよ～！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Okay! Let's go‚ let's go! Actually…\nI made a fishing rod for\n{user}-kun‚ just in case you\ncame back!",
